# EAES Agent Instructions

Follow `AGENTS.md` for all work (mirrored at repo root and `Web/AGENTS.md`).

## Required references

1. **`AGENTS.md`** / **`Web/AGENTS.md`** — workflow, conflict handling, audit rules, UI skill paths, technical defaults (keep mirrors identical).
2. **`PRD_V1.md`** / **`Web/PRD_V1.md`** — authoritative scope and requirements when it conflicts with existing code.
3. **`PRD_PROGRESS_AUDIT.md`** / **`Web/PRD_PROGRESS_AUDIT.md`** — implementation status; update when progress materially changes.

After editing any of the above, update the paired copy or run `.\scripts\sync-mirrored-docs.ps1` (see `mirrored-docs-sync` rule).

## Before implementing

- Read the relevant `PRD_V1.md` sections for the task.
- Check `PRD_PROGRESS_AUDIT.md` for current status and gaps.
- Do not mark PRD items **Done** without evidence (migrations, routes, tests, or verifiable behavior).

## After implementing

- If status changed, update only the affected rows in `PRD_PROGRESS_AUDIT.md` in the same task.
- If the user request conflicted with the PRD and was explicitly overridden, log it under **Off-PRD / Deviations**.

## Laravel

- Application code lives in `Web/`. Run `composer` and `artisan` from that directory.
